கொழுவ  
5. (சது.) to give a sign by a gesture  
to gesticulate  
சைகைகாட்ட.note. this word is used with the ablative of place. அவளோடேசருவுகிறான். he begins to take liberties with her. அவனோடேசருவுகிறான். he falls on him. சருவிக்கொண்டுபேசுகிறான். he speaks fond ly  
or softly  
in courtship